long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Side By Side provides an enhanced Google search experience. When you include "side by side" in your search terms, this extension will provide side by side images at the top of the search results for easy comparison.

Try searching "LeBron James Drake side by side" to see the famous basketball player next to the famous rapper.
Try searching "Petco Park PNC Park side by side" to compare two of America's most scenic ballparks.
Try searching "New York Beijing side by side" to take in two breathtaking city skylines.
Try searching "Anteater Aardvark side by side" to learn the difference between the two animals.
Try searching "Dachshund Poodle Labrador Retriever side by side" to compare your 3 favorite dog breeds.

The options are endless, start today!
